      "title": "ENHANCING GREEN TRUST THROUGH BLOCKCHAIN-ENABLED VERIFICATION: A STUDY ON RTD BIRD'S NEST CONSUMPTION INTENTION AMONG GEN Z",
      "file": "01_DatVanDe.md",
